parameters:
【Masamune】Ugh, I can't proceed because it's in the
way. How am I supposed to move it?

【Masamune】Does anyone have something to deal with
this?

【Intelligent Goblin】Do you want to proceed? It's
probably impossible for foolish-looking people
like you.

【Intelligent Goblin】If you want a hint, fight me
and prove yourself.

【Intelligent Goblin】Hmm... You're quite skilled.
It turns out I was the one being generous.

【Intelligent Goblin】I guess I have no choice but
to tell you. To dissolve the monster blocking the
door, you need to pour sour fruit that grows
outside.

【Intelligent Goblin】To dissolve the monster
blocking the door, you just need to pour sour
fruit that grows outside.
